<p>
  <span class="nym">Erasmus</span>
  <span class="gen">m.</span>
  
  <span class="etym"><span class="lang">Ancient Greek</span> <i>ἐράσμιος</i> 'pleasant'.
  </span>
  
</p>
  
<div class="usg">
  <p>The name of a 4th C saint and the adopted name of an important 15th-16th C Dutch humanist philosopher.</p>
</div>
  
  
  


